  "detailed_description": "<strong>So you’ve been arrested? In Vacant’s Mine you can regain your freedom in just 7 Days!</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>NAVIGATE THROUGH THE MINE</strong></h2></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/7caa198f544eeaa6bc33d1b3f8fe52be.poster.avif?t=1747733865\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/7caa198f544eeaa6bc33d1b3f8fe52be.webm?t=1747733865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/7caa198f544eeaa6bc33d1b3f8fe52be.mp4?t=1747733865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You’ve been arrested. But In this prison camp, you can regain freedom in just 7 days! Navigate an old mine using a railway and steal whatever eggs the stingy and ominous man named Vacant requires. Don’t even think about running out, you’ve got limited electricity!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIND THE EGGS AND STEAL THEM!</strong></h2></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/2b0133543bf626b6418b3014a071ba96.poster.avif?t=1747733865\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/2b0133543bf626b6418b3014a071ba96.webm?t=1747733865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/2b0133543bf626b6418b3014a071ba96.mp4?t=1747733865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use the Railway’s navigation system, manipulate conjunctions, move bridges and try to stay covered in light while you make your way through the cave to the Greebs' nests. But note, Mr. Vacant requires different eggs everyday!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIGURE OUT WHAT HAPPENED AND LOOT SCRAP</strong></h2></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/75a2e70b230338cc59eab81f66ed14d8.poster.avif?t=1747733865\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/75a2e70b230338cc59eab81f66ed14d8.webm?t=1747733865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/75a2e70b230338cc59eab81f66ed14d8.mp4?t=1747733865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Watch, listen and read terminal logs left behind from the miners, who experienced the horror of the Greebs outbreak, before the mine turned into a prison camp to gain information about the egg positions. Keep an eye out to loot some old scrap to upgrade your Mine Railway! <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>AVOID THE GREEBS</strong></h2></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/43f85ec3ceb8fd4214cc9aa3161dbf52.poster.avif?t=1747733865\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/43f85ec3ceb8fd4214cc9aa3161dbf52.webm?t=1747733865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/43f85ec3ceb8fd4214cc9aa3161dbf52.mp4?t=1747733865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Steal the eggs with a Plunger and bring them to Mr. Vacant to regain your freedom. But watch out for the bloodthirsty Greebs!",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>So you’ve been arrested? In Vacant’s Mine you can regain your freedom in just 7 Days!</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>NAVIGATE THROUGH THE MINE</strong></h2></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/7caa198f544eeaa6bc33d1b3f8fe52be.poster.avif?t=1747733865\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/7caa198f544eeaa6bc33d1b3f8fe52be.webm?t=1747733865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/7caa198f544eeaa6bc33d1b3f8fe52be.mp4?t=1747733865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You’ve been arrested. But In this prison camp, you can regain freedom in just 7 days! Navigate an old mine using a railway and steal whatever eggs the stingy and ominous man named Vacant requires. Don’t even think about running out, you’ve got limited electricity!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIND THE EGGS AND STEAL THEM!</strong></h2></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/2b0133543bf626b6418b3014a071ba96.poster.avif?t=1747733865\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/2b0133543bf626b6418b3014a071ba96.webm?t=1747733865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/2b0133543bf626b6418b3014a071ba96.mp4?t=1747733865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use the Railway’s navigation system, manipulate conjunctions, move bridges and try to stay covered in light while you make your way through the cave to the Greebs' nests. But note, Mr. Vacant requires different eggs everyday!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIGURE OUT WHAT HAPPENED AND LOOT SCRAP</strong></h2></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/75a2e70b230338cc59eab81f66ed14d8.poster.avif?t=1747733865\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/75a2e70b230338cc59eab81f66ed14d8.webm?t=1747733865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/75a2e70b230338cc59eab81f66ed14d8.mp4?t=1747733865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Watch, listen and read terminal logs left behind from the miners, who experienced the horror of the Greebs outbreak, before the mine turned into a prison camp to gain information about the egg positions. Keep an eye out to loot some old scrap to upgrade your Mine Railway! <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>AVOID THE GREEBS</strong></h2></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/43f85ec3ceb8fd4214cc9aa3161dbf52.poster.avif?t=1747733865\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/43f85ec3ceb8fd4214cc9aa3161dbf52.webm?t=1747733865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2819940/extras/43f85ec3ceb8fd4214cc9aa3161dbf52.mp4?t=1747733865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Steal the eggs with a Plunger and bring them to Mr. Vacant to regain your freedom. But watch out for the bloodthirsty Greebs!",
